															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226153" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;" >sirpudding</a></span> <span class="odate time_1469035017 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">20 Jul 2016 17:16</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2540965">
									

<blockquote>
<p>No action was taken initially,</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Starting with this clause is evocative, but not informative, and definitely feels like fiction writing. Rather it might be better to write this in chronological order, and note when during the crisis action was taken and by whom.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>By the end of the day, the death toll was in the thousands.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>A range of estimated casualties (or the number if known precisely at this point) would make this more official seeming.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Reports and video evidence came leaking in from several countries in the Northern Hemisphere of giant, stationary 'UFOs' in the sky.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This probably could be expanded a bit. When did these reports start? How were they leaked? Is anything being done to control spin? Is anything being done to control leaks?</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Assessment Team-743 &quot;Snow Blind&quot; was deployed to study the anomaly.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>When? By whom? Was there a security council meeting? Was the General Secretary briefed? What was the legal authority for this order? Remember this is the political part of the report, and politicians always want to know who to blame and how to CYA if it goes pear-shaped.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>It was then that the team observed Foundation forces aboard the SCPS Quarantine performing their own investigation.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Probably should mention that they encountered the <em>Quarantine</em> first, and then what they observed the Foundation doing.</p>
<p>In general a clearer sense of the timeline would be good, it doesn't necessarily need specific times, but some sense of the length of the crisis and how quickly or slowly the responses and developments were would be good.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Jäeger Bombers</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I still don't especially like this nickname, but I guess that's just me.</p>

							</div>

								
