			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2542122">
									

<p>Definitely improved, and upvoted; though personally I would still like to see more of the political side, as the fact that the GOC has to operate politically as a coalition is probably its most interesting distinction from the extralegal Foundation, IMO and also because in the real world use of force isn't valid without accompying legal authority. No real UN peacekeeping operation would ever not include the resolution that justified it.</p>

